chunks.original_latin:
Ex   Prooemio expositionis Evangelii in
Matthaeum. III. Erat namque primum necessarium nobis, ut
unigenitus Deus nostri causa homo, id quod tum non
erat, gigneretur.
chunks.cleaned_english_translation: From the Introduction to the Commentary on the Gospel of Matthew, Chapter 3. It was necessary for us that the only-begotten God became human for our sake, which He was not before.
